snippet.title: 【Tokyo Xtreme Racer】#8：Full PV
snippet.description:
Your rivals await to drag you back into the ultimate challenge! Thrilling races that unfold on the Tokyo Expressway, a return to the Tokyo Xtreme Racer roots. 

We’re back! Coming soon to Steam®. Wishlist now!

『Tokyo Xtreme Racer』Don't miss the first series title in 18 years.
